---
// Place at: src/pages/privacy.astro
import BaseHead from '../components/BaseHead.astro';
import Header from '../components/Header.astro';
import Footer from '../components/Footer.astro';
import { SITE_TITLE } from '../consts';
const updated = 'June 23, 2026';
---

<html lang="en">
  <head>
    <BaseHead title={`Privacy Policy | ${SITE_TITLE}`} description="Privacy policy for Good Morning Pics." />
  </head>
  <body>
    <Header />
    <main>
      <h1>Privacy Policy</h1>
      <p class="updated">Last updated: {updated}</p>

      <p>
        Good Morning Pics ("we," "us") is a daily good-morning art website operated by
        BrianOnAI LLC. We can be reached at <a href="mailto:hello@goodmorning.pics">hello@goodmorning.pics</a>.
        This policy explains what limited information is involved when you visit goodmorning.pics.
      </p>

      <h2>Information we collect</h2>
      <p>
        Good Morning Pics is a simple static website. We do not have user accounts, and we do
        not ask you to submit personal information through forms on this site. We do not sell
        any information.
      </p>
      <p>
        Like nearly all websites, our hosting provider automatically logs standard technical
        information when pages are requested — such as IP address, browser type, and the pages
        viewed — for security and to keep the site running. We also use Google Analytics (GA4)
        to understand, in aggregate, which pages are popular and where our visitors come from
        (for example, search engines or Pinterest).
      </p>

      <h2>Cookies</h2>
      <p>
        Google Analytics sets cookies to measure site usage. You can control or block cookies
        through your browser settings, and you can opt out of Google Analytics across all sites
        using Google's <a href="https://tools.google.com/dlpage/gaoptout" rel="noopener">opt-out
        browser add-on</a>.
      </p>

      <h2>Third-party services</h2>
      <p>
        We rely on a few third parties to operate and measure this site, including our website
        host, Google Analytics, search engines (such as Google and Bing), and Pinterest, where
        we share our daily images. These services have their own privacy policies governing
        their use of information.
      </p>

      <h2>Affiliated links disclosure</h2>
      <p>
        Some pages link to our sister brands — Dragonfly Supply, day9.coffee, and ChiliStation —
        and to products on third-party sites. Some of those links may be affiliate links, meaning
        we may earn a small commission if you make a purchase, at no extra cost to you. We only
        link to things we genuinely stand behind.
      </p>

      <h2>Children's privacy</h2>
      <p>
        This site is general-audience and is not directed to children under 13, and we do not
        knowingly collect personal information from children.
      </p>

      <h2>Changes to this policy</h2>
      <p>
        We may update this policy from time to time; the "last updated" date above will reflect
        any changes.
      </p>

      <h2>Contact</h2>
      <p>
        Questions about this policy? Email <a href="mailto:hello@goodmorning.pics">hello@goodmorning.pics</a>.
      </p>

      <p class="note">
        This page is provided for general information and is not legal advice. Consider having a
        professional review it for your specific circumstances.
      </p>
    </main>
    <Footer />
  </body>
</html>

<style>
  main { width: 720px; max-width: calc(100% - 2em); margin: auto; padding: 2em 1em; }
  h1 { margin: 0 0 0.25em; }
  h2 { margin: 1.5em 0 0.4em; font-size: 1.2em; }
  p { color: rgb(var(--gray-dark)); line-height: 1.7; }
  .updated { color: rgb(var(--gray)); margin-top: 0; }
  .note { color: rgb(var(--gray)); font-size: 0.9em; font-style: italic; margin-top: 2em; }
</style>
